			<CASNumber>Not applicable</CASNumber>
			<common:generalComment xml:lang="en">Recycle Bricks are blocks that have been given a second life through recycling. They are a reliable building material used in construction for creating walls, chimneys, and firepits. These bricks are weather resistant, aesthetically appealing, and highly fire-resistant. They are heavy and bulky landfill material, so it's recommended to reuse them whenever possible. They can be recycled in several ways, such as being chipped and used in landscapes or crushed into very fine material to replace sand or go into new bricks.</common:generalComment>
			<common:generalComment xml:lang="zh">回收砖是通过回收利用获得第二次生命的砖块。它们是一种可靠的建筑材料，可用于建造墙壁、烟囱和壁炉。这些砖具有耐候性、美观性和高度耐火性。它们是笨重的垃圾填埋材料，因此建议尽可能重复使用。它们可以通过多种方式进行回收利用，例如切碎后用于景观设计，或碾碎成非常细的材料来代替沙子或制成新砖。</common:generalComment>
